WEBVTT

01:36.960 --> 01:40.950
[The Best Thing]

01:41.360 --> 01:48.600
[Episode 22: Kudzu Flower]
[Sweet in taste and cold in nature.
It's good for your spleen and stomach, relieving hangovers and bleeding.]

01:53.530 --> 01:54.780
Cheers.

01:58.880 --> 02:00.280
You're just taking a tiny sip?

02:02.010 --> 02:03.090
I'll just drink a little.

02:03.150 --> 02:04.310
If I drink too much,

02:04.340 --> 02:06.290
He Suye might take advantage of it again.

02:06.700 --> 02:08.430
You two better just have a small drink.

02:10.690 --> 02:12.420
Time flies so fast though.

02:12.750 --> 02:13.960
At this time last year,

02:13.960 --> 02:15.860
I was still anxious about the IT summit.

02:16.120 --> 02:17.000
That was the first major event

02:17.000 --> 02:19.180
after I became the Front Office manager.

02:19.360 --> 02:21.079
I had no clue what to do back then.

02:21.310 --> 02:22.420
Now you've got it figured out.

02:22.750 --> 02:24.000
You're already experienced.

02:24.000 --> 02:25.690
You even dare to come out for a drink.

02:26.360 --> 02:27.190
Back then, you were still

02:27.190 --> 02:28.870
anxious about that Mr. Yan.

02:29.300 --> 02:30.160
Don‚Äôt mention it.

02:30.190 --> 02:31.590
It's over. Let's move past it.

02:32.340 --> 02:33.500
When are you going to resign?

02:35.800 --> 02:36.920
Probably in June or July.

02:37.079 --> 02:37.680
But when I go back,

02:37.680 --> 02:39.360
I need to check my study abroad fund.

02:39.500 --> 02:41.380
If it's not enough for living expenses,

02:41.829 --> 02:43.829
I might need a few more big events.

02:43.860 --> 02:44.600
I need the bonuses.

02:44.770 --> 02:45.450
No problem.

02:45.930 --> 02:46.800
No, no, no.

02:46.800 --> 02:48.870
Please, no more big events.

02:48.870 --> 02:50.870
I hate big events the most.

02:50.870 --> 02:53.030
I have to have meetings with the Finance Department every day.

02:53.340 --> 02:54.270
I just want to

02:54.290 --> 02:56.250
coast through these few months and resign with you.

02:59.079 --> 03:00.240
That new job of yours,

03:00.280 --> 03:01.080
the MCN company

03:01.080 --> 03:02.310
you mentioned last time,

03:02.310 --> 03:03.630
I think it's a bit unreliable.

03:04.110 --> 03:05.790
If you want to be a food blogger,

03:05.810 --> 03:07.950
I think you should find a more established company.

03:08.020 --> 03:10.940
I know, okay? Many companies want me.

03:10.960 --> 03:12.080
I'm still choosing.

03:13.190 --> 03:14.340
I'll shut up, then.

03:19.930 --> 03:22.710
In the blink of an eye, we've been working together for seven years.

03:23.600 --> 03:25.030
Time really flies.

03:25.750 --> 03:26.990
Once you two leave,

03:27.310 --> 03:29.000
I'll be left alone at Gunan Huating Hotel.

03:29.000 --> 03:30.450
Isn't that a bit too miserable for me?

03:30.480 --> 03:31.890
Why don't you resign too?

03:31.910 --> 03:33.400
If I resign, we'll both be broke.

03:33.430 --> 03:34.710
Your new job isn't confirmed yet.

03:34.710 --> 03:36.050
I have to earn money to support the family.

03:40.850 --> 03:42.000
I'm still here,

03:42.000 --> 03:42.750
you two.

03:42.750 --> 03:43.430
So what if you're here?

03:43.430 --> 03:44.870
We're family anyway.

03:44.870 --> 03:45.310
Right, right, right.

03:45.310 --> 03:46.030
You're right.

03:46.030 --> 03:46.960
I'm the third wheel, aren't I?

03:47.480 --> 03:48.680
How's your guy doing?

03:51.040 --> 03:51.960
Probably working overtime.

04:42.480 --> 04:43.480
Are you finished?

04:44.220 --> 04:45.220
Do you want me to pick you up?

05:07.070 --> 05:08.110
Why are you still here?

05:08.980 --> 05:09.810
I'm revising the report.

05:10.190 --> 05:10.950
Revising the report?

05:10.950 --> 05:11.750
Why do you have to do it here?

05:11.750 --> 05:12.870
Can't you do it at home?

05:13.680 --> 05:15.240
You don't understand, do you?

05:15.830 --> 05:16.920
After work,

05:17.790 --> 05:19.000
I just want to date.

05:19.250 --> 05:20.910
How can I focus on revising the report?

05:21.190 --> 05:21.910
He,

05:22.440 --> 05:23.220
please get lost.

05:26.560 --> 05:27.020
Alright.

05:27.270 --> 05:28.000
Then...

05:28.860 --> 05:29.740
I'll get lost.

05:30.510 --> 05:31.720
Have a good shift.

05:31.870 --> 05:33.280
Get lost quickly.

05:34.860 --> 05:36.230
How can you be like this?

05:57.990 --> 05:58.820
Hey, Comrade.

05:59.560 --> 06:00.650
Hello, Senior Lin.

06:01.390 --> 06:02.520
Are you guys done?

06:02.880 --> 06:04.000
Do you want me to come and find you?

06:05.360 --> 06:06.190
Xifan has already gone home.

06:06.190 --> 06:06.950
She said she was tired.

06:09.790 --> 06:11.080
Why didn't she reply to my message?

06:12.520 --> 06:14.520
She just sent a WeChat message saying she's home.

06:14.940 --> 06:15.890
Maybe she fell asleep.

06:16.740 --> 06:18.380
Oh, okay.

06:19.890 --> 06:21.010
She didn't drink too much, did she?

06:21.240 --> 06:23.120
She didn't drink much, saying she was afraid you'd trick her.

06:23.150 --> 06:24.830
She didn't even drink half a bottle of beer tonight.

06:26.390 --> 06:27.790
She tells you guys everything.

06:29.560 --> 06:31.900
Alright, let's meet up next time we're free.

06:32.030 --> 06:33.870
Okay, let's meet up next time. Bye.

06:33.900 --> 06:34.340
Okay.

06:34.820 --> 06:35.300
Bye-bye.

07:13.890 --> 07:14.720
Xifan?

07:16.460 --> 07:17.780
Why are you here?

07:21.800 --> 07:23.530
You came to my place without telling me?

07:23.550 --> 07:24.820
I could have come back earlier.

07:25.390 --> 07:27.390
I thought you were working overtime,

07:27.390 --> 07:28.460
so I just waited for you at home.

07:29.300 --> 07:30.330
I had something come up suddenly.

07:30.800 --> 07:32.080
I'll drink with you guys next time.

07:34.610 --> 07:35.520
What was it?

07:38.610 --> 07:39.610
I can't say yet.

07:40.790 --> 07:42.280
I'll tell you when the result comes out next week.

07:43.680 --> 07:44.510
Alright.

07:47.720 --> 07:48.750
Did you draw this?

07:50.590 --> 07:51.500
What did you draw?

07:53.400 --> 07:54.080
You.

07:54.480 --> 07:55.190
Me?

07:56.080 --> 07:56.960
Cute.

07:57.070 --> 07:57.870
Isn't it?

07:58.620 --> 07:59.330
What about these leaves?

07:59.360 --> 08:00.330
What do the leaves mean?

08:03.350 --> 08:04.030
I'm not telling you.

08:05.520 --> 08:08.700
‚ôęNever know what to do‚ôę

08:06.270 --> 08:07.240
Keeping me in suspense.

08:08.000 --> 08:08.680
Tell me.

08:08.700 --> 08:09.510
I won't.

08:08.890 --> 08:12.200
‚ôęIn the times, I'm with you‚ôę

08:09.560 --> 08:10.000
Tell me.

08:10.000 --> 08:10.560
I won't.

08:10.560 --> 08:11.270
Are you going to tell me or not?

08:11.270 --> 08:11.750
I won't tell.

08:11.750 --> 08:12.360
Are you going to tell me or not?

08:12.360 --> 08:12.830
I won't tell.

08:12.830 --> 08:13.480
If you don't tell, I'll bite you.

08:13.480 --> 08:14.160
Then bite me.

08:14.160 --> 08:15.270
I won't tell, I won't tell.

08:16.180 --> 08:19.220
‚ôęNever know what to say‚ôę

08:16.320 --> 08:16.870
Are you going to tell me or not?

08:16.920 --> 08:17.430
I won't tell.

08:18.160 --> 08:19.050
I won't tell.

08:19.500 --> 08:23.590
‚ôęIn the hours, I'm with you‚ôę

08:26.810 --> 08:30.090
‚ôęAll I know, that it's true‚ôę

08:32.510 --> 08:34.909
‚ôęThat it's true‚ôę

08:37.850 --> 08:40.909
‚ôęThat I find myself‚ôę

08:49.390 --> 08:50.630
Suye.

08:52.610 --> 08:54.490
I need you so much.

08:55.360 --> 08:56.290
Did you know?

08:56.500 --> 08:58.770
Fang Kexin ran off with another man.

09:02.100 --> 09:03.820
If you don't want me,

09:04.460 --> 09:06.310
then no one will.

09:11.740 --> 09:12.540
He Suye.

09:15.580 --> 09:16.580
Get me some water.

09:48.130 --> 09:50.100
How does he have your house's password?

09:50.440 --> 09:51.040
Well,

09:51.070 --> 09:52.310
once...

09:53.390 --> 09:54.600
I'll change the password tonight.

09:55.480 --> 09:57.720
Alright, take care of him tonight.

09:57.720 --> 09:58.240
I'm leaving.

09:58.240 --> 09:59.270
It's okay, I'll just...

09:59.270 --> 09:59.960
Okay.

10:00.200 --> 10:01.010
Change the password.

10:01.050 --> 10:01.910
Take care of him.

10:02.050 --> 10:02.600
Go on.

10:09.240 --> 10:09.920
I'm off.

10:27.410 --> 10:28.320
He Suye,

10:29.150 --> 10:29.880
where's the water?

11:25.360 --> 11:26.790
Good morning.

11:31.300 --> 11:32.570
You're having breakfast?

11:37.670 --> 11:38.550
Is there any for me?

11:49.650 --> 11:51.010
I changed the password to the door.

11:51.040 --> 11:52.440
Don't come to my house again.

11:53.850 --> 11:55.510
You can't do this.

11:56.290 --> 11:58.620
When you asked me to game with you before,

11:59.020 --> 12:00.490
I was always there for you.

12:11.960 --> 12:14.080
Was Manager Shen here yesterday?

12:25.250 --> 12:26.470
Eat up, eat up.

12:34.000 --> 12:34.960
Tell me about it.

12:35.080 --> 12:36.910
Why did you get so drunk last night?

12:37.190 --> 12:38.420
What happened between you and Fang?

12:39.660 --> 12:40.490
How did you know?

12:40.890 --> 12:42.890
You told me yourself. How else would I know?

12:51.130 --> 12:52.890
She's dating a senior from school now.

12:54.310 --> 12:55.030
Did she tell you?

12:55.160 --> 12:55.940
No.

12:56.300 --> 12:58.860
I saw them leaving work and going home together.

13:00.510 --> 13:01.840
She didn't even tell you.

13:01.840 --> 13:03.200
How do you know it's true?

13:04.480 --> 13:07.080
They even took a cab together. How can it not be true?

13:10.200 --> 13:11.410
What did I tell you before?

13:12.390 --> 13:15.550
You need to identify the source of the problem before you can operate and remove the tumor.

13:16.720 --> 13:17.360
She didn't even tell you

13:17.360 --> 13:18.270
and you didn't even ask for clarification.

13:18.270 --> 13:19.390
How can you jump to conclusions?

13:22.140 --> 13:23.860
If you're really too afraid to ask her directly,

13:23.890 --> 13:26.290
you can at least ask her friends and colleagues.

13:27.290 --> 13:28.250
Come on.

13:31.240 --> 13:32.950
Your situation is much better than mine was.

13:34.550 --> 13:36.000
Back then, I could only ask her directly.

13:36.000 --> 13:37.840
I didn't know anyone around her.

13:39.570 --> 13:41.020
You mean you and Manager Shen?

13:41.750 --> 13:42.750
Who else?

13:47.000 --> 13:49.310
Everything I'm telling you comes from experience.

13:49.330 --> 13:50.490
You need to listen and take it to heart.

13:53.360 --> 13:53.870
Alright.

13:54.600 --> 13:55.550
Let me think about it.

14:11.730 --> 14:12.500
Eat.

14:28.210 --> 14:29.370
It hurts so much.

14:31.910 --> 14:36.020
[Honganmen Clinic]

14:45.810 --> 14:46.520
Ms. Wu,

14:46.960 --> 14:48.030
can you get me some kudzu flowers?

14:48.430 --> 14:49.020
You've been drinking?

14:49.540 --> 14:50.810
I haven't been drinking.

14:52.480 --> 14:53.200
I see.

14:53.200 --> 14:54.600
Someone has.

15:01.270 --> 15:02.080
It's almost lunch break.

15:15.280 --> 15:16.390
Alright, add water.

15:16.550 --> 15:17.040
Thank you.

15:26.060 --> 15:27.630
My head hurts so much.

15:27.930 --> 15:30.600
Did I drink bad alcohol yesterday?

15:30.930 --> 15:32.080
Help me.

15:35.790 --> 15:36.880
Kudzu flower water.

15:37.660 --> 15:39.030
I knew you drank bad alcohol.

15:39.050 --> 15:40.960
Drink some of this. It can help with the hangover.

15:51.650 --> 15:53.380
Are you coming to my place tonight?

15:55.250 --> 15:55.960
No.

15:56.250 --> 15:56.890
Why not?

15:56.920 --> 15:57.750
Aren't you working overtime?

15:57.770 --> 15:58.800
I don't have to.

15:58.830 --> 16:01.030
No, you have to work this overtime.

16:01.480 --> 16:02.790
Besides, didn't you say

16:02.930 --> 16:04.810
you're busy with something great?

16:04.840 --> 16:05.960
Let's talk after you're done.

16:07.550 --> 16:08.360
Are you angry?

16:08.590 --> 16:09.320
No, I'm not.

16:10.270 --> 16:10.870
Alright.

16:11.550 --> 16:13.360
Then I won't force you.

16:18.710 --> 16:19.880
You changed your profile picture.

16:19.900 --> 16:20.610
Do you like it?

16:20.640 --> 16:22.360
Yeah, isn't it cute?

16:24.270 --> 16:25.480
Why don't you draw one for yourself?

16:25.500 --> 16:26.450
We can have matching pictures.

16:26.650 --> 16:29.600
Sure, I'll draw one when I get home tonight.

16:29.630 --> 16:30.230
Okay.

16:33.640 --> 16:35.470
My artistic skills are really good.

16:35.740 --> 16:37.100
This looks exactly like you.

16:37.120 --> 16:38.640
It really suits you perfectly.

16:38.840 --> 16:40.200
I also think it suits me.

17:13.089 --> 17:16.270
[Shen Xifan]

17:22.599 --> 17:23.400
Where are you?

17:23.490 --> 17:24.650
I'm at home writing my thesis.

17:26.180 --> 17:28.210
Is it convenient for me to come over now?

17:33.320 --> 17:34.560
Sure, come on over.

17:35.000 --> 17:35.640
Okay.

17:36.940 --> 17:37.490
Oh, by the way...

17:39.670 --> 17:40.400
The new password.

17:40.420 --> 17:41.660
It's the last six digits of your phone number.

17:42.640 --> 17:43.270
No problem.

17:43.760 --> 17:44.410
See you later.

17:45.790 --> 17:46.650
See you later.

18:40.310 --> 18:41.470
Hi, handsome.

18:54.470 --> 18:55.880
Mr. Shen's cooking is really good.

18:56.560 --> 18:58.640
My dad knows you've been working hard lately.

18:58.680 --> 18:59.550
He made soup especially

18:59.550 --> 19:00.400
to help you replenish your energy.

19:01.180 --> 19:02.140
He's so good to me.

19:44.970 --> 19:45.490
It's sweet.

19:48.950 --> 19:51.190
Why don't you stay tonight?

19:52.660 --> 19:54.830
It depends on a certain someone's performance.

19:56.080 --> 19:56.930
Don't go.

20:21.090 --> 20:22.850
You're still busy at this hour?

20:24.600 --> 20:25.950
I'm organizing some materials.

20:25.980 --> 20:27.220
I need to go see my grandpa tomorrow.

20:29.720 --> 20:31.400
You've been so secretive lately.

20:31.400 --> 20:32.830
What are you busy with?

20:36.590 --> 20:37.840
Let me keep it a secret for two more days.

20:38.130 --> 20:39.570
If it doesn't work out,

20:39.600 --> 20:40.750
I'll be embarrassed.

20:41.840 --> 20:43.120
I'll tell you when I get the results, okay?

20:45.100 --> 20:45.970
Alright.

20:46.550 --> 20:47.700
Then I'm going out to have some fun.

21:13.790 --> 21:18.300
[Research on TCM-Based Therapy to Improve Quality of Life for Late-Stage Breast Cancer Patients]

21:43.870 --> 21:45.390
It's okay, Suye.

21:45.920 --> 21:46.920
I don't feel unwell.

21:47.650 --> 21:50.320
The doctor said I look much better today.

21:51.360 --> 21:52.600
Don't worry.

22:16.800 --> 22:21.590
[Email sent successfully]

22:50.670 --> 22:51.360
Kexin.

22:53.420 --> 22:54.220
Li Jie.

22:54.940 --> 22:55.510
What's up?

22:57.720 --> 22:59.930
The other day, I saw you at the hospital entrance,

22:59.960 --> 23:01.470
walking away with a guy.

23:01.610 --> 23:02.400
Who was he?

23:03.480 --> 23:04.240
A guy?

23:06.190 --> 23:07.880
That was Senior Chen from the Internal Medicine department.

23:08.210 --> 23:10.050
We went to attend our supervisor's lecture that day

23:10.080 --> 23:11.240
and shared a ride.

23:13.030 --> 23:14.000
Shared a ride?

23:15.630 --> 23:16.360
What's wrong?

23:16.380 --> 23:17.470
Nothing, nothing.

23:18.330 --> 23:20.920
The thesis defense is coming up. How's your paper going?

23:21.930 --> 23:24.410
My writing will never have problems.

23:24.980 --> 23:26.070
After our defense,

23:26.090 --> 23:27.490
why don't we all go out for a meal together?

23:27.530 --> 23:28.130
Sounds good.

23:28.350 --> 23:30.560
I'm transferring to the branch institute in Ning City next semester.

23:31.000 --> 23:32.850
My supervisor opened a research center there

23:32.880 --> 23:33.950
and wants me to go help out.

23:37.260 --> 23:38.110
I'm running late.

23:38.110 --> 23:39.070
I'd better go now.

23:39.350 --> 23:40.020
See you in a couple of days.

23:40.040 --> 23:40.530
Bye-bye.

23:41.130 --> 23:41.770
Bye-bye.

24:01.410 --> 24:04.750
[Invitation to the 8th Chinese Medical Association Summit]

24:16.920 --> 24:18.890
Manager Shen, you should leave work early today

24:19.360 --> 24:20.750
and have a nice date tonight.

24:23.610 --> 24:26.000
Is this what you've been busy with lately?

24:27.200 --> 24:27.960
Yes, it is.

24:49.840 --> 24:51.880
I wish I hadn't asked.

24:52.920 --> 24:53.720
About what?

24:55.760 --> 24:58.000
Fang is transferring to Ning City next semester.

24:59.570 --> 25:00.770
Isn't that good?

25:03.680 --> 25:04.520
Well,

25:04.920 --> 25:06.080
is Fang and I

25:06.110 --> 25:07.870
what they call "not meant to be?"

25:09.990 --> 25:11.470
I don't know if you're meant to be or not,

25:11.490 --> 25:12.980
but you might want to take a look at this first.

25:17.860 --> 25:19.690
Our research report has been approved?

25:21.760 --> 25:22.590
So, does that mean

25:22.590 --> 25:24.510
I now have a paper for a top summit?

25:24.890 --> 25:26.290
Even though I'm not the first author,

25:26.550 --> 25:27.720
my parents won't have to say

25:27.720 --> 25:29.290
I'm not studying hard anymore.

25:29.310 --> 25:31.140
I need to send a picture right away.

25:37.400 --> 25:38.640
This is awesome.

25:43.620 --> 25:44.690
Congratulations.

25:44.940 --> 25:47.980
I'll go back and tell Nian this news later.

25:48.000 --> 25:49.650
She'll be very pleased.

25:58.360 --> 25:59.360
Pretty impressive, huh?

26:23.000 --> 26:23.770
Xifan.

26:31.710 --> 26:35.340
‚ôęWhen I see you‚ôę

26:35.450 --> 26:38.210
Dr. He, why are you glowing?

26:37.470 --> 26:40.200
‚ôęFlowers bloom‚ôę

26:38.920 --> 26:40.240
Oh, it's the glow of wisdom.

26:41.070 --> 26:42.160
Of course it is.

26:41.390 --> 26:45.100
‚ôęWhen I see you‚ôę

26:44.870 --> 26:45.660
What are you hiding?

26:46.590 --> 26:47.270
Don't move.

26:46.940 --> 26:50.170
‚ôęFlowers bloom‚ôę

26:48.550 --> 26:49.420
What are you hiding?

26:52.720 --> 26:53.720
Such a big bouquet of flowers.

26:53.720 --> 26:54.550
Do you like it?

26:54.910 --> 26:55.830
It's beautiful.

26:56.880 --> 26:59.080
Well, since you've given me such a big bouquet,

26:57.590 --> 27:01.050
‚ôęAnd I don't even know where else to go‚ôę

26:59.110 --> 27:00.830
I'll do whatever you want tonight.

27:02.130 --> 27:03.440
I want to have dinner with you,

27:03.470 --> 27:04.670
then go for a walk.

27:04.880 --> 27:06.360
You've been too busy lately.

27:06.380 --> 27:08.540
We haven't had time to talk properly.

27:07.250 --> 27:10.790
‚ôęAnd I don't even know where else to go‚ôę

27:09.400 --> 27:11.560
Dinner, shopping, chatting.

27:12.150 --> 27:13.000
What else?

27:29.320 --> 27:30.000
That's all.

27:32.720 --> 27:34.350
What are you thinking, He Suye?

27:33.570 --> 27:40.950
‚ôęNothing in this world can take me away from you‚ôę

27:34.370 --> 27:35.170
You hurt me. You can't.

27:35.200 --> 27:35.790
I didn't.

27:35.790 --> 27:36.750
You need to make it up to me tonight.

27:36.750 --> 27:37.790
I did it lightly.

27:40.490 --> 27:41.140
You agreed, right?

27:41.270 --> 27:41.880
No way.

27:42.640 --> 27:43.440
You agreed.

27:43.270 --> 27:50.390
‚ôęNothing in this world can take me away from you‚ôę

27:43.470 --> 27:44.190
In your dreams.

27:58.780 --> 27:59.820
Are you done staring?

28:02.990 --> 28:04.270
I was just thinking...

28:04.480 --> 28:07.500
When you're at the summit with those old TCM doctors,

28:07.790 --> 28:09.030
if others ask me,

28:09.400 --> 28:11.290
"Which one is your boyfriend?",

28:11.320 --> 28:12.670
I'll point and say, "Look.

28:12.690 --> 28:14.300
He's the most handsome one there."

28:21.650 --> 28:22.250
That's it?

28:24.130 --> 28:25.960
Why don't you compliment my academic level?

28:26.460 --> 28:28.830
This event is a top-notch academic exchange.

28:30.400 --> 28:31.050
Alright.

28:31.750 --> 28:33.020
Actually, I've seen

28:33.130 --> 28:35.610
the list of attendees staying at the hotel for this summit.

28:36.070 --> 28:38.810
They're all very senior doctors in Chinese and Western medicine.

28:39.530 --> 28:42.680
The fact that your report was selected for presentation

28:42.700 --> 28:44.220
shows that your professional level

28:44.250 --> 28:45.730
is undoubtedly high.

28:45.750 --> 28:47.340
I can compliment you now‚ÄĒ

28:48.230 --> 28:49.230
you're like an old TCM physician.

28:50.220 --> 28:51.990
Do you have to add the word "old"?

28:55.360 --> 28:57.120
But honestly,

28:57.440 --> 28:58.720
thank you for

28:58.840 --> 29:00.400
being understanding during this time.

29:01.330 --> 29:03.200
Of course. I know

29:03.230 --> 29:05.640
this opportunity is really important to you.

29:07.510 --> 29:08.870
Actually, I'm quite surprised.

29:09.270 --> 29:10.840
After all, this topic before...

29:10.870 --> 29:11.390
Stop.

29:11.810 --> 29:13.340
How can you call this a surprise?

29:13.620 --> 29:15.700
You've been working on this topic since last year, right?

29:17.300 --> 29:20.230
Exactly. This shows it's the result of your hard work.

29:23.750 --> 29:24.850
You don't know,

29:24.990 --> 29:27.350
but when your project was suspended before,

29:27.410 --> 29:28.780
I was struggling,

29:28.810 --> 29:30.680
not knowing how to comfort you.

29:30.700 --> 29:32.790
So your success this time

29:32.820 --> 29:34.240
actually makes me happier than you.

29:35.000 --> 29:35.750
Cheers!

29:36.650 --> 29:37.930
We can't do bottoms up with this.

29:45.130 --> 29:47.560
Will you be here for the entire event?

29:49.350 --> 29:50.400
Besides presenting my topic,

29:50.400 --> 29:51.240
I'll also participate in several

29:51.260 --> 29:53.180
academic exchanges and specialized forums.

29:54.180 --> 29:56.140
Oh, my grandpa will be coming too.

29:56.180 --> 29:57.450
He'll be speaking as a TCM representative

29:57.480 --> 29:58.650
at the opening ceremony.

30:03.800 --> 30:04.600
So,

30:05.330 --> 30:07.370
will you be staying at our hotel?

30:07.590 --> 30:08.560
I probably won't.

30:08.590 --> 30:10.020
Our association doesn't have that much budget.

30:10.610 --> 30:11.570
Local doctors

30:11.600 --> 30:12.610
will all stay at home

30:12.640 --> 30:14.220
to ease the pressure on the association.

30:16.090 --> 30:16.930
Fine.

30:17.250 --> 30:17.860
What?

30:18.200 --> 30:20.370
Do you want me to stay at your hotel?

30:21.220 --> 30:22.280
I didn't say that.

30:22.790 --> 30:25.160
One less guest means less pressure for me.

30:25.570 --> 30:27.660
Besides, our hotel has a rule

30:27.890 --> 30:30.650
that guests and staff must maintain a safe distance.

30:31.620 --> 30:32.920
With our relationship,

30:32.920 --> 30:33.940
do we also need to keep a safe distance?

30:34.120 --> 30:36.000
Of course, I'm very professional.

30:36.310 --> 30:37.150
In the hotel,

30:37.170 --> 30:37.850
you have to stay

30:37.880 --> 30:39.400
10 meters away from me.

30:39.680 --> 30:40.310
Alright.

30:41.070 --> 30:41.920
Well, I'd like to see

30:41.920 --> 30:42.880
if our Manager Shen

30:42.910 --> 30:44.110
can really manage to

30:44.130 --> 30:45.800
keep a 10-meter safe distance from me.

30:46.160 --> 30:46.960
Of course I can.

31:00.440 --> 31:01.380
Have you had breakfast?

31:01.510 --> 31:02.660
It'll take an hour to get there.

31:02.740 --> 31:03.800
I've eaten. Let's go.

31:07.500 --> 31:08.150
By the way,

31:08.800 --> 31:10.640
your father will also attend as a representative

31:10.660 --> 31:11.950
of cardiac surgery experts.

31:12.510 --> 31:14.840
He'll be giving a special report at the meeting.

31:16.680 --> 31:18.680
If you're free,

31:19.990 --> 31:21.300
why don't you chat with him?

31:24.610 --> 31:25.400
We'll see.

31:25.430 --> 31:26.120
Let's go now.

31:34.720 --> 31:37.030
The guests for today's Chinese Medical Association Summit

31:37.030 --> 31:38.110
are about to enter.

31:38.130 --> 31:39.650
All departments, please prepare accordingly.

31:40.050 --> 31:42.100
Food & Beverage, assist with the food supply.

31:42.800 --> 31:45.470
Pay special attention to the sanitation of the dining area.

31:45.630 --> 31:46.470
No problem.

31:48.520 --> 31:50.280
Add salt and pepper.

31:50.300 --> 31:51.290
Wipe it first.

31:56.330 --> 31:58.610
Marketing Department, help manage the order in the venue.

31:58.630 --> 32:00.830
Be proactive in preventing and responding to any emergencies.

32:01.400 --> 32:03.270
Mr. Lin, please take extra care during the summit.

32:03.650 --> 32:04.300
Understood.

32:10.200 --> 32:11.440
Those arriving on the first day of the summit

32:11.470 --> 32:12.780
are all VIP guests.

32:12.800 --> 32:14.190
Everyone needs to pay special attention.

32:15.090 --> 32:17.020
[The 8th Summer Summit of the Chinese Medical Association]

32:17.050 --> 32:18.720
[Marketing Department] [Food & Beverage Department] [Front Office Department]

32:17.270 --> 32:19.880
Manager Shen from the Front Office, please ensure proper guest guidance

32:19.880 --> 32:21.910
and handle any room-related issues for the staying guests.

32:21.940 --> 32:22.830
Received.

32:23.340 --> 32:24.610
Alright, let's get moving.

32:27.950 --> 32:28.640
Thank you for your trouble.

32:28.640 --> 32:29.450
I'll ask them to confirm again.

32:43.310 --> 32:44.380
This way, please.

32:45.420 --> 32:46.220
Hello.

32:47.720 --> 32:48.240
Hello, hello.

32:48.240 --> 32:49.110
Welcome, welcome.

32:50.030 --> 32:51.160
Hello, hello, hello.

32:51.160 --> 32:51.830
Welcome.

32:51.860 --> 32:54.380
The elevators are over there. Please watch your step.

32:57.240 --> 32:58.090
Where's Shen?

32:58.910 --> 33:00.150
She shouldn't be here, right?

33:00.290 --> 33:02.290
Didn't you say she's the Front Office Manager?

33:02.510 --> 33:04.400
The Front Office Manager has a wide range of responsibilities.

33:04.400 --> 33:05.550
It's not just about the lobby.

33:06.720 --> 33:07.160
Right.

33:07.510 --> 33:09.030
Three, two.

33:09.070 --> 33:09.830
Okay, thank you.

33:09.830 --> 33:10.200
Look at the camera.

33:10.200 --> 33:10.790
Alright, let's go.

33:16.540 --> 33:17.830
We need to add a standard room now.

33:17.830 --> 33:19.300
Just put it in 8602.

33:19.330 --> 33:20.270
If there's anything else,

33:20.270 --> 33:21.160
just call me directly.

33:21.160 --> 33:22.030
Alright, understood, Manager.

33:22.030 --> 33:22.680
I'll go attend to my duties now.

33:22.700 --> 33:23.380
Thank you for your hard work.

33:26.630 --> 33:34.060
‚ôęLove love love love, is right in front of me‚ôę

33:26.960 --> 33:27.640
Hello.

33:27.640 --> 33:28.590
Welcome.

33:34.740 --> 33:42.430
‚ôęOoh love, ooh love, I've seen your face‚ôę

33:43.000 --> 33:50.250
‚ôęLove love love love, is talking right at me‚ôę

33:50.480 --> 33:57.420
‚ôęLoving you, loving you, is the best thing I'll ever do‚ôę

33:59.830 --> 34:00.440
Professor Yu.

34:01.330 --> 34:02.640
Hello, Shen.

34:02.660 --> 34:03.510
Hello.

34:03.540 --> 34:04.560
You must be busy.

34:04.710 --> 34:05.470
It's not too bad.

34:05.500 --> 34:07.780
This is much more relaxed compared to large commercial events.

34:08.100 --> 34:09.270
Where are you two heading?

34:10.350 --> 34:11.540
We're going to the opening ceremony.

34:11.810 --> 34:13.040
The main venue is over here.

34:13.070 --> 34:13.949
I'll take you there.

34:13.969 --> 34:14.699
No need.

34:14.960 --> 34:15.590
We're family.

34:15.590 --> 34:16.580
Don't trouble yourself.

34:20.639 --> 34:23.560
Feel free to contact us when you're not busy.

34:23.580 --> 34:24.980
That's enough, Grandpa.

34:26.170 --> 34:27.040
No problem.

34:27.900 --> 34:29.010
Then, this way, please.

34:29.030 --> 34:30.760
Alright, alright.

34:35.920 --> 34:36.760
Today,

34:37.330 --> 34:38.210
