34:42.110 --> 34:42.699
Go away.

35:02.730 --> 35:03.210
Hello.

35:03.240 --> 35:03.760
Hello.

35:03.760 --> 35:05.110
Are you here for the summit?

35:05.110 --> 35:06.510
I need to go to the main venue.

35:06.730 --> 35:07.690
The main venue is this way.

35:07.710 --> 35:08.400
I'll take you there.

35:08.430 --> 35:09.630
No, just tell me where it is.

35:09.630 --> 35:10.720
I can go by myself.

35:10.880 --> 35:12.430
It's no trouble. It's our job.

35:12.450 --> 35:13.250
Let me carry your suitcase for you.

35:14.500 --> 35:15.350
You're too kind.

35:15.370 --> 35:16.120
This way, please.

35:16.150 --> 35:16.920
Thank you.

35:23.620 --> 35:24.270
It's alright.

35:24.810 --> 35:26.370
We still have five minutes. We'll make it.

35:26.910 --> 35:28.460
It is a bit rushed, isn't it?

35:31.830 --> 35:32.400
Professor He.

35:32.430 --> 35:33.470
You've come too.

35:33.940 --> 35:34.710
I've heard so much about you.

35:34.730 --> 35:35.640
Long time no see.

35:35.670 --> 35:36.190
Long time no see.

35:36.210 --> 35:37.210
How are things on your end?

35:37.510 --> 35:38.150
Quite busy now.

35:38.150 --> 35:39.000
Things are going well, right?

35:39.000 --> 35:39.710
Not bad.

35:39.990 --> 35:42.760
Your report is really good.

35:43.740 --> 35:44.940
That was just a rush job.

35:45.270 --> 35:46.100
I'm sorry.

35:46.430 --> 35:48.560
Sorry, Professor He.

35:48.590 --> 35:49.440
It's almost time.

35:49.440 --> 35:50.320
You need to go in now.

35:50.920 --> 35:51.710
Let's chat another day then.

35:51.710 --> 35:51.880
Alright.

35:51.880 --> 35:52.400
Let's talk another day.

35:52.400 --> 35:52.760
You go ahead.

35:52.760 --> 35:53.960
Let's find time to have a good chat.

35:54.110 --> 35:54.990
Sure, sure.

35:55.120 --> 35:56.120
This is the check-in area.

36:01.840 --> 36:02.720
Thank you.

36:05.590 --> 36:06.590
Thank you, young lady.

36:06.840 --> 36:07.800
Sorry for the trouble.

36:08.310 --> 36:09.500
It's our job.

36:09.590 --> 36:10.440
I wish you all the best.

36:10.440 --> 36:10.960
Okay.

36:19.390 --> 36:20.500
Distinguished leaders,

36:19.440 --> 36:23.100
[The 8th Summer Summit of the Chinese Medical Association]

36:21.100 --> 36:22.390
experts,

36:22.770 --> 36:24.080
and colleagues,

36:24.580 --> 36:26.460
good morning.

36:31.480 --> 36:32.850
I'm very happy

36:33.070 --> 36:34.190
to be invited

36:34.190 --> 36:35.400
to participate in

36:35.560 --> 36:37.600
the 8th Summer Summit of

36:37.780 --> 36:39.900
the Chinese Medical Association.

36:40.830 --> 36:41.590
As an

36:41.590 --> 36:45.110
elderly practitioner who has been engaged in TCM clinical work for a long time,

36:45.380 --> 36:48.050
I'm very excited and happy.

36:48.880 --> 36:50.400
Through the summit agenda,

36:50.700 --> 36:51.550
I see that

36:51.840 --> 36:53.000
TCM has made

36:53.190 --> 36:56.990
significant contributions in disease treatment.

36:57.280 --> 36:59.550
I've also noticed at the venue that‚Ä¶

36:59.800 --> 37:00.550
What's the plan for lunch?

37:00.550 --> 37:02.760
There's a considerable number of young people.

37:03.150 --> 37:04.510
What does this indicate?

37:04.880 --> 37:09.230
It shows that the TCM cause is being passed down continuously.

37:09.230 --> 37:10.880
Meeting a few TCM professors with Grandpa

37:10.880 --> 37:11.920
and having a meal together.

37:16.230 --> 37:18.140
So I sincerely hope

37:18.190 --> 37:20.590
that those in the TCM field

37:21.510 --> 37:22.800
-Okay.
-will work together

37:23.710 --> 37:25.400
to forge ahead

37:26.070 --> 37:29.880
and strive to carry forward the TCM cause.

37:30.550 --> 37:33.320
Wish the summit a success. Thank you.

37:38.800 --> 37:41.430
Thank you, Professor Yu Liren, for your excellent speech.

37:41.680 --> 37:44.030
As a leading figure in the field of TCM,

37:44.060 --> 37:45.830
Professor Yu has made outstanding contributions

37:45.880 --> 37:47.420
to the development of TCM.

37:47.840 --> 37:48.440
Alright,

37:48.440 --> 37:50.840
next, let's welcome

37:50.840 --> 37:52.840
Professor Li from Jiangzhou University of TCM to give a speech.

37:56.980 --> 37:59.190
Madam, this contains lavender,

37:59.210 --> 38:00.410
which is especially good for women.

38:01.540 --> 38:02.460
Please enjoy, both of you.

38:05.680 --> 38:06.460
Mr. He.

38:07.760 --> 38:09.630
This is a special gift prepared by our hotel for you,

38:09.630 --> 38:11.320
a small sachet.

38:12.930 --> 38:14.250
What's inside it?

38:14.510 --> 38:16.180
Yours contains fennel.

38:17.720 --> 38:19.110
I just tried your medicated diet.

38:19.140 --> 38:20.430
It is quite good.

38:20.450 --> 38:21.480
This porridge especially

38:22.010 --> 38:23.050
has a very special taste.

38:23.880 --> 38:24.990
I'm glad you like it.

38:25.010 --> 38:27.130
It was specially designed by our TCM consultant.

38:27.160 --> 38:28.850
The herbs inside are very carefully chosen.

38:28.920 --> 38:30.090
Good, good, good.

38:30.290 --> 38:30.960
Please enjoy your meal.

38:30.990 --> 38:31.560
Alright.

38:37.630 --> 38:38.700
Dr. He.

38:38.940 --> 38:40.010
Is everyone here for lunch?

38:40.040 --> 38:40.630
Please, come this way.

38:40.630 --> 38:41.190
Grandpa,

38:41.330 --> 38:42.930
this is a friend of mine and Shen's.

38:42.960 --> 38:44.190
I know Xu.

38:44.210 --> 38:45.210
I've taken her pulse before.

38:45.230 --> 38:46.040
Don't you remember?

38:46.590 --> 38:47.590
Yes, yes.

38:48.200 --> 38:50.200
She also led the medicated diet project last time.

38:51.450 --> 38:52.570
There are seats over here.

38:52.600 --> 38:53.930
Alright, thank you.

38:54.300 --> 38:56.900
These two are TCM experts from Su City.

38:58.000 --> 38:59.480
Well, since you're all experts,

38:59.480 --> 39:00.440
I'll refrain from showing off.

39:00.440 --> 39:01.480
I won't introduce the medicated diet.

39:01.920 --> 39:02.990
Just tell me what you'd like to eat

39:03.010 --> 39:03.820
and I'll get it for you.

39:03.850 --> 39:04.810
Okay, sure.

39:05.880 --> 39:06.550
Welcome.

39:10.370 --> 39:11.870
He Suye, turn around.

39:20.320 --> 39:21.060
Grandpa,

39:21.310 --> 39:22.140
Shen is looking for me.

39:22.160 --> 39:22.930
I'll step out for a moment.

39:22.960 --> 39:23.880
Go ahead.

39:24.810 --> 39:25.450
Just a moment.

39:31.720 --> 39:32.820
Why are you here?

39:32.980 --> 39:34.060
Come with me for a moment.

39:53.760 --> 39:54.950
Why did you come now?

39:55.620 --> 39:56.500
Have you eaten?

39:56.520 --> 39:57.290
I've already eaten.

39:57.600 --> 39:58.710
I missed you.

39:59.560 --> 40:00.770
What are your plans later?

40:01.410 --> 40:03.300
I'll attend a few lectures later,

40:03.330 --> 40:04.560
have tea with the old TCM practitioners,

40:05.950 --> 40:06.800
and wait for you to get off work.

40:08.560 --> 40:11.000
You probably won't be able to wait until I get off work today.

40:11.480 --> 40:13.040
I have to work overtime tonight.

40:13.650 --> 40:15.610
You should go back and keep Professor Yu company.

40:17.270 --> 40:18.500
Wait for me at home tonight.

40:19.750 --> 40:21.180
Alright, see you at home.

40:23.550 --> 40:24.320
By the way,

40:24.620 --> 40:25.580
well,

40:25.600 --> 40:27.070
my father is here too.

40:27.100 --> 40:28.270
Could you take care of him for me?

40:29.310 --> 40:30.580
Sure, no problem.

40:30.860 --> 40:32.220
Which room is he staying in?

40:32.250 --> 40:33.160
I don't know.

40:33.760 --> 40:34.760
His name is He Sheng.

40:34.780 --> 40:35.740
Okay.

40:35.770 --> 40:37.930
I'll go check discreetly.

40:40.910 --> 40:42.020
Manager Shen,

40:42.760 --> 40:44.510
can you come to the venue now?

40:46.010 --> 40:46.820
Okay.

40:46.850 --> 40:48.120
Got it, I'm coming now.

40:49.280 --> 40:50.470
I need to go now.

40:51.930 --> 40:52.860
I'm leaving then.

40:54.650 --> 40:55.260
Wait.

40:57.290 --> 40:57.960
What?

41:03.790 --> 41:04.430
Go ahead.

41:06.370 --> 41:07.370
I'm going then.

41:07.920 --> 41:08.990
Think of me.

41:09.270 --> 41:09.940
I'm leaving.

41:47.500 --> 41:48.020
Hello.

41:48.070 --> 41:48.670
Hello.

41:48.670 --> 41:50.030
Are you here for the summit?

41:50.060 --> 41:51.270
I need to go to the main venue.

41:51.700 --> 41:52.740
The main venue is this way.

41:52.800 --> 41:53.480
I'll take you there.

41:53.480 --> 41:53.940
No need.

41:53.960 --> 41:54.810
Just tell me where it is.

41:54.840 --> 41:55.880
I can find it myself.
